  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张图来说明教育内容分发网络（Education ContentCDN）的依赖关系。核心问题是：开发者团队要部署应用，但他们其实不直接接触CDN，而是通过一套CommonConfig来间接关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Developer",
        "CommonConfig"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那Developer和Infrastructure之间是什么关系？是部署依赖还是配置读取？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Developer需要Infrastructure提供的基础资源，同时他们也要对接Kubernetes做容器编排。但关键点在于：CommonConfig是中枢——Infrastructure和Kubernetes都要向它同步配置，而Application最终通过CommonConfig才能回连到Education_ContentCDN获取内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes",
        "CommonConfig",
        "Application",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我梳理一下：Developer连Infrastructure和Kubernetes；Infrastructure和Kubernetes都连CommonConfig；CommonConfig再连Application；Application最后连回Education_ContentCDN。这样形成一条从人到基础设施再到内容分发的链路，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes",
        "CommonConfig",
        "Application",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但漏了一个细节：CommonConfig和Kubernetes之间其实是双向的，配置中心要下发配置给K8s，K8s也会上报状态回去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommonConfig",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上双向关系。另外Developer到CommonConfig也有直接连线吗？还是只通过Infrastructure和Kubernetes间接关联？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "CommonConfig",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Developer可以直接读取CommonConfig，这是日常调试的快捷路径。所以Developer要直接连CommonConfig，而不是绕一圈。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "CommonConfig"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整：Developer直接关联CommonConfig，同时保留和Infrastructure、Kubernetes的连接。双向的CommonConfig-Kubernetes关系也已标注。整张图的依赖闭环应该完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
